# Local / machine-specific / regenerable graphify state — do not commit.
# The repo-root .gitignore is the authoritative, cross-branch source of truth
# for this policy; these entries mirror it so the rules also apply on branches
# that predate the root block. Tracked deliverables (graph.json, GRAPH_REPORT.md,
# manifest.json, wiki/) are intentionally NOT listed here.
.graphify_python
.graphify_root
.graphify_labels.json
cost.json
cache/
# Deterministic vis.js render of graph.json — free to rebuild via
# `graphify export html`, and `graphify update` deletes it above 5000 nodes.
graph.html
# Per-run dated snapshot archives (YYYY-MM-DD/) — regenerated, not tracked.
[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]/
